Kevin Chamberlin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Chamberlin 0 Kevin Chamberlin (born November 25, 1963) is an American actor. He is known for his theatre roles such as Horton in Seussical and Fester in The Addams Family. He also starred as Bertram Winkle in the Disney Channel Original Series sitcom Jessie from 2011 to 2015. He is currently starring as the Wizard in Wicked on Broadway. Kevin_Chamberlin ( born November_25_,_1963 ) is an_American_actor .
